            {"text": "{{architectid}}", "bold": true},
            " is appointed by me/us and is authorized to make representation/application with regard to aforesaid construction to any of the authorities."
          ],
          "alignment": "justify"
        },
        {
          "text": [
            "I/We further declare that I am/We are aware of all the action taken or representation made by the ", {"text": " {{architectName}} {{architecttype}}", "bold": true}," authorized by me/us."
          ],
          "alignment": "justify",
          "margin": [0, 0, 0, 10]
        },
        {
          "ol": [
            "That I am/We are sole owner of the site.",
            "There is no dispute regarding the site and if any dispute arises then I shall be solely responsible for the same.",
            "That construction of the building will be undertaken as per the approved building plans and structural design given by the Structural Engineer."
          ],
          "alignment": "justify",
          "margin": [20, 0, 0, 10]
        },
        {
          "text": "That above stated facts are true and all the requisite documents uploaded with this E-Naksha plan have been signed by the owner/owners in my presence",
          "margin": [0, 0, 0, 25]
        },
        {
          "columns": [
            {
              "width": "*",
              "alignment": "right",
              "stack": [
                {"text": ["Name of Owner : ", {"text": "{{name}}", "bold": true}]},
                {"text": ["Application Number : ", {"text": "{{applicationNo}}", "bold": true}]},
                {"text": ["Mobile : ", {"text": "{{mobileNumber}}", "bold": true}]},
                {"text": ["Signature : ", {"text": "Verified by OTP at {{otpverifiedtimeowner}}", "bold": true}]}
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "styles": {
